sentence: Joe Kent, a Trump-backed Army Special Forces veteran prolific on social media and conservative talk shows, appeared to come closer to matching the fund-raising totals of his opponent, Representative Jaime Herrera Beutler of Washington, but still trailed her in both quarterly hauls and cash on hand.
title: Republicans Who Voted to Impeach Trump Out-Raised Primary Rivals

sentence: Republican women's group Maggie's List has thrown its support behind Rep. Jaime Herrera Beutler (R-Wash.) as part of its latest round of endorsements first obtained by The Hill on Wednesday.
author: Julia Manchester
title: GOP women's group endorses Herrera Beutler in primary race

sentence: In Washington state, Rep. Jaime Herrera Beutler raised $605,000, while Trump-backed former Green Beret Joe Kent raised $457,000.
author: Herb Jackson
title: Trump targets outraise challengers, unlike some other incumbents
